spec_data.Name: php-pear-Auth-SASL
spec_data.Description:
Provides code to generate responses to common SASL mechanisms, including:
o Digest-MD5
o CramMD5
o Plain
o Anonymous
o Login (Pseudo mechanism)

spec_data.Summary: Abstraction of various SASL mechanism responses
